{"title":"mysql的case-when-then-else-end","date":"2018-04-12T12:33:01.000Z","slug":"mysql的case-when-then-else-end","comments":true,"tags":["case","else","end","mysql","then","when"],"categories":["mysql"],"updated":"2019-03-29T03:42:01.000Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><h2 id=\"两种基本语法\"><a href=\"#两种基本语法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"两种基本语法\"></a>两种基本语法</h2><ul><li>简单函数：</li></ul><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">CASE 字段名 WHEN 值1 THEN 结果1 WHEN 值2 THEN 结果2 ELSE 其他结果 <span class=\"keyword\">END</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>简单函数的条件只支持 <strong>字段名 = 值</strong> 的情况，且始终是同一个字段，对于多个字段或者 <strong>IN</strong>，<strong>!=</strong>，这些条件得用下面的搜索函数。</p><ul><li>搜索函数</li></ul><figure class=\"highlight sql\"><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">CASE WHEN 条件1 THEN 结果1 WHEN 条件2 THEN 结果2 ELSE 其他结果 <span class=\"keyword\">END</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>搜索函数可以写判断，并且搜索函数只会返回第一个符合条件的值，其他 <strong>CASE</strong> 被忽略。</p></body></html>","prev":{"title":"oltp和olap","slug":"oltp和olap"},"next":{"title":"正则表达式","slug":"正则表达式"},"link":"/post/mysql的case-when-then-else-end/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"两种基本语法","index":"1"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"license":"原创版权，转载请注明来源 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","author":"沈捷译","link":"<a href=\"/post/mysql的case-when-then-else-end/\" title=\"mysql的case-when-then-else-end\">/post/mysql的case-when-then-else-end/</a>"}}